⁣
“August will be green for me! I will be in my country house near Blois, France. It's really relaxing being surrounded by birdsong and the wind in the trees, a break from my Parisian city life. I love to invite friends round, and the moment of the aperitif is sacred for us, so having a barbecue and visiting the small wine producer near my house is the perfect plan!⁣
⁣
With love,⁣
⁣
Viki”.
